{"id": 1999, "genre": 1001, "title": "你小时候玩过哪些游戏？有什么美妙的回忆？", "description": "来分享一下，游戏曾经陪伴你度过怎样的一段时光。（题图来自：Wikimedia Commons）", "record_count": 2326, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171107162315aVcjY1PARb5mtvEZ.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-11-08T03:00:33Z", "options": [{"id": 265728, "content": "超级马里奥", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1266176}, {"id": 247040, "content": "暗黑破坏神啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1178735}, {"id": 247296, "content": "梦幻模拟战经常看我哥玩……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 879647}, {"id": 247041, "content": "侠盗飞车", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1176317}, {"id": 247297, "content": "贪吃蛇", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1159100}, {"id": 247553, "content": "俄罗斯方块", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1142579}, {"id": 248321, "content": "MC我的世界，在服务器里挺快乐的一段时光.我遇到第一个与我说话的人，一起分享的人，再一起去谈论别的游戏.我们会互相射箭，一起盖房子..", "image": "img/option/option/20171113230935dApxzf2PlqVWRywM", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1182581}, {"id": 247298, "content": "魂斗罗，坦克大战，超级玛丽", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1179716}, {"id": 247043, "content": "绿色兵团，魂斗罗，不动明王传", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1178744}, {"id": 247299, "content": "小霸王插卡那种游戏机基本都玩过 像马戏团超级玛丽魂斗罗之类 后来有电脑玩自带三维弹球喜滋滋 仙剑幻想三国志三国无双极品飞车鬼武者之类 还有侠盗飞车。。以致现在看到高尔夫球场那个车都觉得该去追杀上面的人。。 再后来玩孢子虐杀原形 再后来 就不玩游戏了 也不知道什么时候青春期结束的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1129892}, {"id": 247555, "content": "小人大战。纸上画的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 677668}, {"id": 247811, "content": "松鼠大战，玩的开心的时候，都是扛着伙伴跳。玩的起别扭，就比赛把对方扔河里?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 476124}, {"id": 247044, "content": "魂斗罗.冒险岛.打雪人.坦克.俄罗斯方块.街头霸王.超级玛丽........太多了", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 215999}, {"id": 247300, "content": "超级玛丽。每次他来我家我们都会玩，然后就记得他说:我才不捡金币，我不贪财。\n后来我也默默不捡…  他是我第一个暗恋的男孩子，只是后来他不来我家后我们没联系了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1179717}, {"id": 247045, "content": "好好记得人一生珍惜每一天快乐这活着是感恩，我、\n'听过感恩的心很好听也希望我们都有颗i好心", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1178744}, {"id": 247301, "content": "超级玛丽，死了又玩，玩了又死，阴差阳错救了公主。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1176506}, {"id": 247046, "content": "双截龙", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1178748}, {"id": 247302, "content": "多的数不过来", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 695493}, {"id": 247047, "content": "down", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1176715}, {"id": 247303, "content": "所有任天堂红白机fc上的游戏全是美好的回忆啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1114777}, {"id": 248071, "content": "黄金矿工双人版！抓金子和钻石地鼠！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 703144}, {"id": 247048, "content": "热血篮球", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1178748}, {"id": 247304, "content": "坦克大战无异议了。小时候我爸总是和我一起过关，我只守老巢不出门，我爸就在外面杀敌。哈哈！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1085407}, {"id": 247560, "content": "推箱子…华容道…以前在电子词典上偷偷摸摸的玩", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 892943}, {"id": 247816, "content": "魂斗罗吧，跟我爸一起玩的，话说手柄真心好用啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1181901}, {"id": 247049, "content": "热血系列", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1178748}, {"id": 247305, "content": "坦克大战 小霸王键盘游戏机插卡玩的，每个周末的晚上都会跟老爸老妈在电视机前守护“老爷”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 889583}, {"id": 247050, "content": "忍者龙剑传", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1178748}, {"id": 247306, "content": "老爸带我打魂斗罗 冒险岛 超级玛丽，他各种通关我各种菜\nemmmm....人家是女孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1179816}, {"id": 249354, "content": "超级玛丽 梦幻西游和我老爸送给我老妈的俄罗斯方块游戏机 小学的时候玩的跑跑卡丁车", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1179559}, {"id": 247051, "content": "FC游戏热血系列，满满得都是回忆，感觉热血故事编成动漫也是很不错的选择?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1178752}, {"id": 247307, "content": "红警，造满屏坦克，碾压", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1179822}, {"id": 247563, "content": "植物大战僵尸啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 926785}, {"id": 247052, "content": "超级玛丽…至今记得没关的奖命蘑菇?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118850}, {"id": 247053, "content": "口袋妖怪，牧场物语", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118850}, {"id": 247054, "content": "顶蘑菇\r\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1178748}, {"id": 247055, "content": "玩的恐龙快打", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1178754}, {"id": 247056, "content": "魂斗罗 ，超级玛丽，俄罗斯方块，坦克大战", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1175233}, {"id": 247057, "content": "没人玩过双截龙三部曲嘛?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1164981}, {"id": 247058, "content": "俄罗斯方块，奥特曼", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1166583}, {"id": 247059, "content": "快乐西游，你们不懂的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 801171}, {"id": 247060, "content": "非得暴露我的界别的话我希望它是：猪！小！！弟。拱！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 666852}, {"id": 247061, "content": "我玩忍者神龟pk贼厉害", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 838273}, {"id": 247062, "content": "有人记得守卫剑阁么", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1173704}, {"id": 247063, "content": "gameboy上的马里奥，后来我的gameboy被我表哥骗去了，至今未还??", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 963421}, {"id": 247831, "content": "摩尔庄园和QQ堂", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 957807}, {"id": 247064, "content": "泡泡堂", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1178769}, {"id": 249624, "content": "枕头大战 和哥哥一起\n心疼当时的娃娃三秒钟( ｰ̀εｰ́ )", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1186347}, {"id": 250648, "content": "小时候经常玩的，四。个。大。字。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1191673}, {"id": 247065, "content": "红色警戒！！！！\n好想再玩一次，可惜了。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1147407}]}